  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK310">
<l>iṟantā riṟantā raṉaiyar ciṉattait</l>
<l>tuṟantār tuṟantār tuṇai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those, who give way to excessive anger, are no better than dead men; but those, who are freed from it, are equal to those who are freed (from death).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
